01:13:23,182 --> 01:13:26,185
OH, JEEZ.
LISTEN, IT DOESN'T LOOK AS IF
THERE'S AN AWFUL LOT LEFT.

1318
01:13:26,185 --> 01:13:28,187
IT'S ALL YOU.
ALL FOR ME ?

1319
01:13:28,687 --> 01:13:30,189
THANKS, YOU GUYS.

1320
01:13:30,689 --> 01:13:32,191
[ Sniffing ]

1321
01:13:32,691 --> 01:13:34,193
AHH.
[ Snorts ]

1322
01:13:34,693 --> 01:13:36,695
FUCK.  THAT'S GOOD.
IT'S GOOD STUFF.  SHH.

1323
01:13:36,695 --> 01:13:39,698
LISTEN.  COME HERE.

1324
01:13:39,698 --> 01:13:41,700
WHAT'S SAY
WE MAKE A GO OF THIS...

1325
01:13:42,201 --> 01:13:44,703
AND YOU DROP OFF THE CASH
TOMORROW ?

1326
01:13:46,705 --> 01:13:48,707
THAT'LL DO IT.
YEAH.

1327
01:13:50,209 --> 01:13:52,711
[ Horrace ]
LOOK.  HERE'S WHAT WORRIES ME.

1328
01:13:53,212 --> 01:13:55,714
HE WANTS TO HAVE THIS MEETING
AT THIS BAR IN RED HOOK.

1329
01:13:55,714 --> 01:13:57,716
KNOW WHERE THAT IS ?
NO.

1330
01:13:57,716 --> 01:14:01,220
BROOKLYN.  HE MUST HAVE
THAT SHIT TROUGHED OFF.

1331
01:14:01,220 --> 01:14:03,222
WHAT DO YOU MEAN
"TROUGHED OFF" ?

1332
01:14:03,222 --> 01:14:05,724
[ Horrace ]
PROTECTED LIKE A FORTRESS.

1333
01:14:06,225 --> 01:14:08,727
RUIZ TIED IN
OUT THERE ?
NO.

1334
01:14:08,727 --> 01:14:11,730
PUERTO RICANS
AND IRISH IMMIGRANTS
FRESH OFF THE BOAT.

1335
01:14:12,231 --> 01:14:14,233
HEY, I'M HALF IRISH.

1336
01:14:14,233 --> 01:14:18,237
YOU AIN'T
THIS KINDA FUCKIN' IRISH.
EVER HEARD OF THE WESTIES ?

1337
01:14:18,237 --> 01:14:20,739
YEAH, I HEARD OF THEM.
THEM SOME BAD MOTHERFUCKERS.

1338
01:14:20,739 --> 01:14:22,741
THEY USED TO
CUT PEOPLE'S HEADS OFF,

1339
01:14:22,741 --> 01:14:24,743
LEAVE THEM ON THE BAR,
FINISH THEIR DRINK...

1340
01:14:24,743 --> 01:14:27,746
WHEN THEY WERE
MAKING A PLAY AGAINST
THE ITALIANS IN THE EIGHTIES.

1341
01:14:27,746 --> 01:14:30,249
I'M NOT FUCKIN'
WITH THOSE KIND
OF MOTHERFUCKERS.

1342
01:14:30,249 --> 01:14:33,752
SOUNDS TO ME LIKE EVERYBODY'S
GETTING A LITTLE JUMPY.
YEAH, WHATEVER.

1343
01:14:33,752 --> 01:14:36,755
HE'S GOT NOTHING AT STAKE.
THIS IS JUST A DROP.

1344
01:14:36,755 --> 01:14:40,759
I SAY WE GO TO HIS
"TROUGHED OFF" BAR, DROP OFF
THE BAG LIKE RUIZ SAID...

1345
01:14:40,759 --> 01:14:42,761
AND GET ON A PLANE
 AND GO HOME.

1346
01:14:42,761 --> 01:14:47,766
NOT A WORD TO MAXIE.
MAXIE FINDS OUT WE CROSSED
THE BRIDGE, HE GONNA SHIT.

1347
01:14:48,267 --> 01:14:50,269
[ Door Opens ]
OKAY.

1348
01:14:53,272 --> 01:14:55,774
[ Sighs ]

1349
01:15:07,619 --> 01:15:11,123
HEY, BOBBY, WE'RE HOME.
COME ON.  WAKE UP, WAKE UP.

1350
01:15:11,123 --> 01:15:14,126
GET SOME SLEEP.
LET'S GO GET SOME SLEEP.

1351
01:15:21,633 --> 01:15:24,136
HEY, GUYS.
IT'S, UH, UNCLE BOBBY.

1352
01:15:24,136 --> 01:15:26,138
I'M GONNA BE HOME
REALLY SOON.
[ Beeping ]

1353
01:15:26,138 --> 01:15:29,141
[ Chloe ]
BOBBY ?
CHLOE ?

1354
01:15:29,141 --> 01:15:32,644
UNCLE BOBBY'S GONNA
BE HOME REALLY SOON.
CAN YOU COME HOME, PLEASE ?

1355
01:15:33,145 --> 01:15:37,149
I LOVE YOU.
YEAH, I LOVE YOU, TOO, BABY.
I GOTTA GO.

1356
01:15:39,151 --> 01:15:41,153
[ Chloe ]
I JUST WANT YOU TO BE HERE.

1357
01:15:54,166 --> 01:15:56,668
EVERYTHING IS GOING AS--
YEAH.

1358
01:15:56,668 --> 01:15:59,171
EVERYTHING
IS GOING AS PLANNED.

1359
01:16:00,672 --> 01:16:02,674
IF ANYTHING CHANGES,
I'LL CALL YOU.

1360
01:16:04,676 --> 01:16:07,179
WHERE'S RICKY ?

1361
01:16:07,679 --> 01:16:09,681
RICKY'S TAKEN CARE OF.

1362
01:16:10,682 --> 01:16:15,187
HOW SO ?
HE'S GONNA MEET US DOWN THERE.

1363
01:17:11,743 --> 01:17:14,746
WHERE'S RICKY ?
I DON'T KNOW,
AND I DON'T GIVE A SHIT.

1364
01:17:14,746 --> 01:17:16,748
LET'S JUST TAKE CARE OF THIS.

1365
01:18:06,798 --> 01:18:11,803
[ Crowd Cheering ]
[ Man On TV ]
A FRIENDLY GROUP.  THANK YOU.

1366
01:18:11,803 --> 01:18:13,805
[ Door Creaks ]
[ Man On TV ]
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

1367
01:18:14,306 --> 01:18:17,309
ENJOY YOURSELF.
WELCOME TOWHEEL OF FORTUNE.
GLAD TO HAVE YOU WITH US.

1368
01:18:17,309 --> 01:18:20,312
YOU FOLKS AT HOME
FIGURE OUT THE PREVIEW PUZZLE ?

1369
01:18:20,312 --> 01:18:23,315
LET'S TAKE A LOOK
AND SEE IF YOU WERE RIGHT.

1370
01:18:23,315 --> 01:18:27,319
IT'S EUROPEAN VACATION WEEK,
FEATURING SOME GREAT CARS.

1371
01:18:27,319 --> 01:18:30,822
WE HAVE TRIPS TO THE RIVIERA
AND GERMANY, LONDON AND SPAIN...

1372
01:18:30,822 --> 01:18:33,325
[ TV Audio Fades Out ]

1373
01:18:44,836 --> 01:18:47,339
[ Tom ]
HEY.  HEY, GUYS.

1374
01:18:47,839 --> 01:18:50,342
HEY.
HOW YOU DOING, BOBBY ?

1375
01:18:50,342 --> 01:18:52,344
HOW YOU DOING ?
YOU ALL RIGHT ?

1376
01:18:52,344 --> 01:18:55,347
OH, IT'S ALL RIGHT.
SORRY, GUYS.

1377
01:18:55,347 --> 01:18:57,849
YOU KNOW--
YOU KNOW THE DEAL.
YOU KNOW HOW IT IS.

1378
01:18:57,849 --> 01:19:01,353
YEAH.  SURE.
SO, UH,

1379
01:19:01,353 --> 01:19:03,355
LISTEN,
YOU WANT A DRINK ?

1380
01:19:03,355 --> 01:19:05,857
NAH.

1381
01:19:05,857 --> 01:19:07,859
NO, I'M GONNA
PASS ON THAT.

1382
01:19:08,360 --> 01:19:11,863
[ Tom ]
NO ?  UH, LISTEN, UM,
WHERE'S YOUR MATE ?

1383
01:19:12,864 --> 01:19:15,367
YEAH.
HE-HE WON'T BE WITH US.

1384
01:19:15,367 --> 01:19:18,370
LOOK.  HERE'S, UH--

1385
01:19:18,370 --> 01:19:20,872
HERE'S THE MONEY--
NOT TO RUSH YOU.

1386
01:19:20,872 --> 01:19:24,376
YOU GIVE US THE MARKER,
WE CAN BE ON OUR WAY.

1387
01:19:25,377 --> 01:19:27,879
I'LL HAVE TO COUNT IT,
OTHERWISE...

1388
01:19:28,380 --> 01:19:30,382
I CAN'T VERIFY THE AMOUNT,
YEAH ?

1389
01:19:30,382 --> 01:19:33,885
DON'T WORRY ABOUT THAT.
JUST WRITE DOWN THAT
YOU TOOK A DELIVERY.

1390
01:19:33,885 --> 01:19:36,388
[ Tom ]
SURE.  SURE, MAN.

1391
01:19:36,388 --> 01:19:39,391
- FUCK !  HEY !  HEY !
-[ Horrace ]
 FUCK, MAN !

1392
01:19:39,391 --> 01:19:44,396
- WHAT THE FUCK ARE YOU DOING ?
  WHAT ARE YOU DOING ?
- SHUT THE FUCK UP !

1393
01:19:44,396 --> 01:19:46,898
AH !  YOU FUCKIN' BASTARD !

1394
01:19:46,898 --> 01:19:51,403
ALL RIGHT.  AS FAR AS
ANY OF YOU ARE CONCERNED,
A GANG OF SPICS TOOK THE BAG.

1395
01:19:51,403 --> 01:19:53,405
UNDERSTOOD ?  GOOD.

1396
01:19:53,405 --> 01:19:56,908
- GRAB HIS FUCKIN' WALLET.
- I FUCKIN' HIRED THESE GUYS
  TO WATCH MY BACK.

1397
01:19:56,908 --> 01:19:58,910
WILL YOU SHUT THE FUCK UP ?

1398
01:19:58,910 --> 01:20:01,413
[ Door Creaks ]

1399
01:20:03,915 --> 01:20:05,917
MAYBE YOU SHOULD
SHUT THE FUCK UP.

1400
01:20:12,924 --> 01:20:15,427
ALL RIGHT.  STEADY, GUYS.
TAKE IT EASY.

1401
01:20:15,427 --> 01:20:18,930
HE'S GOT SIX SHOTS.
 HE'S BOUND TO MISS.

1402
01:20:18,930 --> 01:20:20,932
WHAT ARE YOU,
AN ODDSMAKER ?

1403
01:20:20,932 --> 01:20:23,935
YOU GONNA WORK EVERYONE
THROUGH THIS THING HERE ?

1404
01:20:24,436 --> 01:20:25,937
LET ME TELL YOU
SOMETHING, FUCKO.

1405
01:20:25,937 --> 01:20:29,941
IF THAT MOTHERFUCKER RIGHT THERE
DON'T TAKE THAT KNIFE AWAY
FROM MY FRIEND'S NECK,

1406
01:20:30,442 --> 01:20:33,945
I'LL USE ALL SIX SHOTS
TO MAKE SURE YOU'RE DEAD.

1407
01:20:33,945 --> 01:20:35,947
NOW DO YOU
BELIEVE IT ?

1408
01:20:36,448 --> 01:20:38,950
DO YOU FUCKIN' BELIEVE IT ?

1409
01:20:44,956 --> 01:20:48,460
NOW I WANT EVERYONE
TO DROP THEIR BATS
AND TOYS AND--

1410
01:20:48,460 --> 01:20:51,463
- IT'S A STARTER PISTOL.
- WHAT ?

1411
01:20:51,463 --> 01:20:54,466
HIS GUN IS A FUCKIN'
STARTER PISTOL.

1412
01:20:54,466 --> 01:20:57,469
I CAN SEE THE RED PLUG
IN YOUR FUCKIN' BARREL !

1413
01:20:57,969 --> 01:21:02,974
LISTEN TO ME.  I INTENTIONALLY
MAKE THIS GUN LOOK THAT WAY
BECAUSE I AM SMART.

1414
01:21:03,475 --> 01:21:04,976
I DON'T WANNA DRAW--

1415
01:21:27,499 --> 01:21:30,001
THAT'S ENOUGH !
 THAT'S ENOUGH.

1416
01:21:30,502 --> 01:21:33,505
COME BACK HERE, HO.
GET OVER IN THE CORNER,
ALL YOU GUYS.

1417
01:21:33,505 --> 01:21:38,510
GET OVER IN THE CORNER !
DROP YOUR WEAPONS.

1418
01:21:38,510 --> 01:21:41,012
I SAID DROP
YOUR FUCKIN' WEAPONS !

1419
01:21:41,012 --> 01:21:43,014
GET OVER IN THE CORNER.

1420
01:21:43,515 --> 01:21:46,017
OVER IN THE FUCKIN' CORNER !

1421
01:21:46,017 --> 01:21:50,021
TAKE OUT YOUR WALLETS RIGHT NOW.
PUT 'EM ON THE TABLE.

1422
01:21:51,523 --> 01:21:54,025
TURN AROUND.

1423
01:21:54,025 --> 01:21:56,027
TURN AROUND.

1424
01:21:56,027 --> 01:21:58,530
PUT YOUR HANDS
BEHIND YOUR HEAD.

1425
01:22:00,532 --> 01:22:03,535
NOW GET
ON YOUR FUCKIN' KNEES.
GET ON YOUR KNEES !

1426
01:22:08,039 --> 01:22:11,042
BOBBY, COME HERE.
TAKE THAT.

1427
01:22:16,047 --> 01:22:18,550
[ Jimmy ]
NICE WORK, BOBBY.

1428
01:22:18,550 --> 01:22:21,052
I'LL LET MAXIE KNOW
YOU'RE GOOD IN THE POCKET.

1429
01:22:27,559 --> 01:22:30,562
GO HOME.

1430
01:22:54,085 --> 01:22:56,087
[ Motor Starts ]

1431
01:23:05,096 --> 01:23:07,098
YOU KNOW,
 YOU BOYS DID GOOD.

1432
01:23:07,599 --> 01:23:11,102
I NEVER INTENDED TO TEST YOU
TO SUCH AN EXTENT,

1433
01:23:11,102 --> 01:23:13,605
BUT YOU COME THROUGH.

1434
01:23:13,605 --> 01:23:16,107
I COULD'VE USED A CALL.

1435
01:23:16,107 --> 01:23:18,610
RUIZ SAID NOT TO CALL.

1436
01:23:18,610 --> 01:23:21,112
I'LL TAKE THAT UP WITH RUIZ.

1437
01:23:21,613 --> 01:23:24,616
YOU GOT THE MONEY,
THOUGH ?
THE MONEY COME THROUGH.

1438
01:23:24,616 --> 01:23:26,618
I COULD'VE USED A CALL.

1439
01:23:28,119 --> 01:23:30,121
AS FOR YOU, RICKY,
YOUR DRAW,

1440
01:23:30,121 --> 01:23:33,008
THAT'S GONNA GO
TO A NEW CARPET-CLEANING VAN.

1441
01:23:33,008 --> 01:23:36,244
I WALKED INTO A ROOM
FULL OF FUCKIN' WESTIES
FOR THAT.

1442
01:23:36,244 --> 01:23:38,747
IF THEY WERE WESTIES,
YOU'D BE DEAD.

1443
01:23:39,247 --> 01:23:40,749
THAT'S NOT THE POINT.
WE'RE SQUARE.

1444
01:23:41,249 --> 01:23:43,968
AS FOR YOU, BOBBY,

1445
01:23:43,968 --> 01:23:46,471
YOUR DAYS OF FIGHTING
FOR CRUMBS ARE OVER.

1446
01:23:46,471 --> 01:23:50,475
TAKE A WEEK, COME BACK,
WE'LL TALK ABOUT
THE NEXT THING.

1447
01:23:56,981 --> 01:23:59,484
I DON'T THINK THERE'S
GONNA BE A NEXT THING, MAX.

1448
01:23:59,984 --> 01:24:01,986
TAKE A FEW DAYS.

1449
01:24:02,487 --> 01:24:06,491
I DON'T NEED A FEW DAYS.
I'M THROUGH, AND JESS
IS THROUGH DANCING FOR YOU.

1450
01:24:06,991 --> 01:24:09,494
YEAH, WELL,
I HATE TO, UH--

1451
01:24:09,994 --> 01:24:12,997
I HATE TO BREAK UP
YOUR, UH,

1452
01:24:12,997 --> 01:24:16,000
FANTASY DREAM,
OR WHATEVER THE FUCK IT IS,

1453
01:24:16,501 --> 01:24:20,004
BUT I'VE BEEN
PAYING JESSICA'S RENT
FOR EIGHT MONTHS.

1454
01:24:28,012 --> 01:24:32,016
THANK YOU FOR THE OPPORTUNITY.
WE'RE GONNA BE LEAVING NOW.

1455
01:24:44,529 --> 01:24:47,532
[ Sighs ]
OH, GOD.

1456
01:24:47,532 --> 01:24:49,534
MMPH.

1457
01:24:50,535 --> 01:24:52,537
A LOT GOING ON.

1458
01:24:52,537 --> 01:24:56,541
BUT THERE ALWAYS IS,
ISN'T THERE--
A LOT GOING ON ?

1459
01:24:56,541 --> 01:25:00,044
MMM.
I GOTTA TELL YOU,

1460
01:25:02,046 --> 01:25:05,550
I AM SURE GLAD THAT
THAT FUCKIN' VAN
IS OUT OF THE WAY.

1461
01:25:05,550 --> 01:25:08,052
IT WAS HANGING OVER MY HEAD
FOR TOO LONG.

1462
01:25:08,052 --> 01:25:11,055
BOBBY CAN BE
A LITTLE HASTY SOMETIMES.

1463
01:25:11,055 --> 01:25:14,058
YOU SAID WHAT TO HIM ?
"WAIT A FEW DAYS."

1464
01:25:14,559 --> 01:25:18,062
SMART.  LET'S LET HIM
WAIT A FEW DAYS.

1465
01:25:18,062 --> 01:25:23,067
I'M GONNA GO AHEAD
AND HOLD ONTO THIS FOR HIM.
KEEP YOUR HANDS OFF THE MONEY.

1466
01:25:23,067 --> 01:25:25,570
MAYBE HE'LL DECIDE--
OKAY.  OKAY.
DON'T TOUCH THE MONEY !

1467
01:25:26,070 --> 01:25:28,072
LEAVE THE MONEY RIGHT THERE.

1468
01:25:28,573 --> 01:25:30,575
MY POINT BEING--
GET THE FUCK OUT.

1469
01:25:30,575 --> 01:25:34,579
UNDERSTOOD, BUT IF HE CHANGES
HIS MIND, CAN HE COME BACK--
GET THE FUCK OUT.

1470
01:25:34,579 --> 01:25:37,582
OKAY.  OKAY.

1471
01:25:38,082 --> 01:25:40,084
NICE TO SEE YOU.

1472
01:25:42,587 --> 01:25:44,589
ASSHOLE.

1473
01:25:49,093 --> 01:25:51,846
[ Motor Stops ]
I'LL CHECK ON THE GIRLS.

1474
01:25:52,347 --> 01:25:54,933
I'LL BE RIGHT OUT.

1475
01:26:07,445 --> 01:26:09,447
CHLOE ?

1476
01:26:10,448 --> 01:26:15,453
- WHERE'S MOMMY ?
-[ Jess Laughing ]

1477
01:26:26,965 --> 01:26:28,967
[ Chattering ]

1478
01:26:34,472 --> 01:26:36,975
[ Chattering Continues ]

1479
01:26:36,975 --> 01:26:39,978
YOUR--
[ Laughs ]
I JUST--

1480
01:26:41,479 --> 01:26:43,982
WHY DON'T YOU GET YOUR SHIT ?

1481
01:26:45,483 --> 01:26:47,986
[ Clears Throat ]

1482
01:26:58,496 --> 01:27:00,498
[ Clears Throat ]

1483
01:27:05,503 --> 01:27:08,506
I NEVER PROMISED YOU
ANYTHING, OKAY ?

1484
01:27:08,506 --> 01:27:11,009
HOW COULD YOU LET HER
SEE YOU LIKE THIS ?

1485
01:27:14,012 --> 01:27:16,014
BYE, BOBBY.

1486
01:27:18,516 --> 01:27:20,518
[ Sighs ]

1487
01:27:20,518 --> 01:27:25,523
- I BOUGHT YOU OUT WITH MAX
  IN CASE YOU WANNA LEAVE.
- I DON'T WANNA LEAVE.

1488
01:27:25,523 --> 01:27:27,525
YOU DO
WHAT YOU GOTTA DO,

1489
01:27:27,525 --> 01:27:32,030
BUT THAT LITTLE GIRL OUT THERE
IS SUCH A SPECIAL PERSON--

1490
01:27:32,030 --> 01:27:35,533
- TAKE HER.
- WHAT ?

1491
01:27:40,538 --> 01:27:43,041
TAKE HER.

1492
01:27:51,549 --> 01:27:53,551
HEY, CHLOE.

1493
01:27:57,555 --> 01:28:02,560
I JUST TALKED TO YOUR MOM,
AND SHE THOUGHT THAT, UM,

1494
01:28:02,560 --> 01:28:05,563
IT MIGHT BE A GOOD IDEA
IF FOR A LITTLE WHILE...

1495
01:28:05,563 --> 01:28:08,066
MAYBE YOU AND ME
WENT ON A TRIP SOMEPLACE.

1496
01:28:16,574 --> 01:28:19,077
OKAY ?
IS THAT OKAY ?

1497
01:28:20,578 --> 01:28:22,580
YEAH.
WE'RE GONNA GO NOW.

1498
01:28:22,580 --> 01:28:25,083
ALL RIGHT ?
OKAY.

1499
01:28:33,474 --> 01:28:36,427
- THERE'S RICKY.
- HEY, BABY.  HOW ARE YOU ?

1500
01:28:36,427 --> 01:28:39,430
[ Chloe ]
GOOD.
YEAH ?  YOU FEEL GOOD ?

1501
01:28:39,430 --> 01:28:42,433
YEAH.
I DON'T THINK
THEY WERE EXPECTING ME.

1502
01:28:42,433 --> 01:28:45,937
I'M SORRY, MAN.
IS SHE OKAY ?

1503
01:28:45,937 --> 01:28:49,440
YEAH.  I THINK
SHE'S HUNGRY.

1504
01:28:49,941 --> 01:28:52,443
WANNA GET SOMETHING TO EAT ?
GET THE SEAT BELT ON.

1505
01:28:52,443 --> 01:28:55,446
YOU WANNA GO COLOR
SOME THINGS ?  FROGS ?

1506
01:28:55,446 --> 01:28:57,949
UH-UH.
LEOPARDS ?

1507
01:29:00,451 --> 01:29:04,455
- ARE YOU ALL RIGHT, MAN ?
- ME ?  OH, YEAH.
  I'M ALL RIGHT.

1508
01:29:04,455 --> 01:29:06,958
YOU OKAY ?
 YOU SHOULD BE OKAY.
I'M OKAY.

1509
01:29:06,958 --> 01:29:10,461
I'M OKAY.  I'M OKAY.
YOU SHOULD BE.
GOOD.

1510
01:29:10,461 --> 01:29:12,964
- DON'T ASK ME
  IF I'M OKAY AGAIN.
- I'M NOT ASKING YOU.

1511
01:29:13,464 --> 01:29:15,466
LET'S JUST
GET SOME FOOD.
LET'S GET SOME FOOD.

1512
01:29:15,466 --> 01:29:18,970
- I'M NOT OKAY.
-[ Motor Starts ]

1513
01:29:18,970 --> 01:29:21,756
???? [ Country ]

1514
01:29:24,926 --> 01:29:27,345
HERE WE GO.

1515
01:29:27,845 --> 01:29:30,848
?? YOU GOT TO HAVE
  AN ACE IN THE HOLE ??

1516
01:29:30,848 --> 01:29:34,852
?? A LITTLE SECRET
  THAT NOBODY KNOWS ??

1517
01:29:34,852 --> 01:29:37,355
???? [ Singing Continues,
     Indistinct ]

1518
01:29:37,855 --> 01:29:40,858
[ Chloe ]
DID EVERYONE GET CAKE ?

1519
01:29:40,858 --> 01:29:42,860
[ Kids ]
YES !

1520
01:29:42,860 --> 01:29:45,863
LET'S SAY HAPPY BIRTHDAY
TO CHLOE.  GET YOUR TOYS
AND DO YOUR THINGS,

1521
01:29:45,863 --> 01:29:47,865
'CAUSE THE BIG PEOPLE
GOTTA TALK NOW.

1522
